## Objective

Replace the TODO stub in `sendDiscordNotification()` with a working implementation that sends a rich embedded message to a Discord Webhook URL. Messages use Discord's embed format with color coding, structured fields, and a link to the dashboard. The implementation mirrors the Slack integration but uses Discord's API format.

