## Verification

- [ ] `sendDiscordNotification()` sends HTTP POST to webhook URL with correct JSON body
- [ ] Message uses Discord embed format with `embeds` array
- [ ] Color is a decimal number (not hex string)
- [ ] Username overridden to "gBlockParty"
- [ ] Embed fields: project name, event type, status (all inline)
- [ ] Error message included as embed description when present
- [ ] Dashboard link included as embed `url`
- [ ] Footer shows "gBlockParty"
- [ ] Timestamp in ISO 8601 format
- [ ] HTTP 204 treated as success (not just 200)
- [ ] HTTP 429 rate limiting handled with retry
- [ ] Non-2xx response throws error with status and body details
- [ ] Network timeout (10s) enforced
- [ ] No sensitive information in the notification message
- [ ] Error messages truncated to 4096 characters (Discord limit)
